07:11.471 --> 07:16.557
God has a word for you and no word from God will return void.

07:17.258 --> 07:26.770
Isaiah 55 says, as the rain falls from the heaven and waters the earth and causes it to flourish, so will God's word be.

07:27.138 --> 07:28.900
that comes forth from his mouth.

