To Matthew chapter 13.

07:51.370 --> 07:54.034
Matthew chapter 13 verses 31.

07:54.978 --> 07:57.741
32 and Matthew chapter 13 verse 44.

07:59.823 --> 08:05.490
I'm gonna share a little scripture today with you that is really going to help you in your life.

08:06.631 --> 08:23.890
And if while I'm preaching the microphone pops and struggles and strains underneath the weight of this anointing, I will scream so loud that the dude in the back row will fall down the stairs from the shock

