08:39.501 --> 08:41.723
Jesus told them another parable.

08:42.664 --> 08:53.618
He said, the kingdom of heaven is like a mustard seed, which a man took and planted in his field, though it is the smallest of all seeds

08:54.178 --> 09:06.673
